_source.text: 135 missions since April 1981 isn't bad, it is better than Soyuz manned-mission counts in the same timeframe: Soyuz T(16), Soyuz TM (34) and Soyuz TMA (21).

text: 135 missions since April 1981 isn't bad, it **is** **better** **than** Soyuz manned-mission counts in the same timeframe: Soyuz T(16), **Soyuz** **TM** (**34**) and **Soyuz** **TMA** (**21**).
